INSERT INTO `t_article` VALUES (136, 1024, 222, 'http://my-bucket0823.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/aurora/articles/a7799f18551353efd5aebb4d53be2cd7.jpg', '2024-03-01', '一篇关于Java基础的文章', '# Java基础概念\n\n1. 简单易学；面向对象（封装，继承，多态）；\n2. 平台无关性（ Java 虚拟机实现平台无关性）；\n3. 支持多线程（ C++ 语言没有内置的多线程机制，因此必须调用操作系统的多线程功能来进行多线程程序设计，而 Java 语言却提供了多线程支持）；\n4. 可靠性（具备异常处理和自动内存管理机制）；\n5. 安全性（Java 语言本身的设计就提供了多重安全防护机制如访问权限修饰符、限制程序直接访问操作系统资源）；\n6. 高效性（通过 Just In Time 编译器等技术的优化，Java 语言的运行效率还是非常不错的）；\n7. 支持网络编程并且很方便；\n8. 编译与解释并存；\n9. ……\n\n🌈 拓展一下：\n“Write Once, Run Anywhere（一次编写，随处运行）”这句宣传口号，真心经典，流传了好多年！以至于，直到今天，依然有很多人觉得跨平台是 Java 语言最大的优势。实际上，跨平台已经不是 Java 最大的卖点了，各种 JDK 新特性也不是。目前市面上虚拟化技术已经非常成熟，比如你通过 Docker 就很容易实现跨平台了。在我看来，Java 强大的生态才是！\n\n\n', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, '2024-03-01 18:56:42', '2024-04-06 16:21:32');
INSERT INTO `t_article` VALUES (137, 1024, 217, 'https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/aurora/articles/7a74bd647adbbfeb67b05909de1d747b.png', '2024-03-02', '', '# 毕业设计论文\n\n## 任务\n\n\n\n1. 外文翻译 ： 软件开发相关技术文件 近3年不少于2000字  每个人一份\n2. 毕设任务书：，大背景，数据分析\n3. 需求分析：具体需求分析 用例图\n4. 技术的学习数据手机与处理\n\n\n\n## 课题详情\n\n### **课题内容介绍**\n\n轻博客系统由用户管理子系统、博文管理子系统、数据分析子系统构成。\n\n博客管理主要包括博文信息的管理，博文基本信息管理、博文浏览、博文推荐、系统首页设置模块、博文推荐、分类管理、标签管理等功能。\n\n\n\n```\n1.	研究方法\n首先对项目内容进行需求的分析，然后进行系统设计，包括系统架构的设计、功能模块设计、数据库的设计、系统界面的设计等。然后进行技术的研究，对项目进行相关的技术选型，并且学习相关的技术。\n2.	分析思路\n对课题任务逐项分析，找出重难点，由易到难。首先先将简单的部分完成比如博文的基础信息管理等，将项目的整体部分实现，由于项目模块清晰在完成后在进行相关的技术的升级。最后克服重难点实现整个项目。\n3.	技术路线\n首先整个项目的架构为B/S架构，前端是Web的页面程序，后端部署在Linux上，采用前后端分离的方式。使用Vue框架构建前端的界面，Vue采用响应式设计，确保在不同设备上都能提供良好的用户体验，并且编码效率高，维护容易，解决方案多。后端采用的方案是SpringBoot作为开发的框架，MyBayis 作为ORM框架，这是现在比较流行的后端框架学习成本低，方案简单，开发效率很高。\n4.	重难点解决方案\n\n```\n\n\n\n### **论文（设计）要求**\n\n（1）与组内其他2名同学合作完成需求分析、系统界面的设计与实现；\n\n（2）博文信息管理实现对博文基本信息的增删改查及权限管理；分类管理和标签管理实现博文信息的分类管理；\n\n（3）针对博文浏览功能，要求对信息搜索常用的方法进行学习、汇总，并选取合适的算法运用到博文查找模块设计中；\n\n（4）博文推荐要求能够学习协同过滤算法，实现不同的推荐方法；\n\n（5）系统首页设置模块要求选取合适模板，开发，实现对博文网站的布局管理。\n\n（6） 对系统进行实现和测试，包括功能测试和性能测试等；\n\n（7）完成毕业设计论文的撰写工作。\n\n\n\n\n\n###  开题报告\n\n选题背景：系统的意义，系统几部分构成(说明负责的部分，方便管理，查找意义)。\n\n国内外现状：每个人的能力不同\n\n主要的内容：整个系统的内容，在介绍自己的内容\n\n![image-20240301194809169](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2024/03/01/056006760f87e579194558d7d6b05654-2651b1.png)\n\n\n\n方案与计划\n\n参考文献 10个；\n\n开题答辩 答辩的时候写\n', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-03-02 16:46:53', '2024-03-02 20:14:27');
INSERT INTO `t_article` VALUES (138, 1024, NULL, NULL, 'vue模板配置', NULL, '# vue模板配置\r\n\r\n- node：16.14.2   vue：3.2.xx  IDE:vscode\r\n\r\n## 1. 创建VUE\r\n\r\n- 使用 **命令vue ui** 开始创建（最好在项目文件夹下开启命令行）\r\n\r\n![image-20221117144948343](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/eb9a7ee816741c0d3bca090cf5970fb0-f4834b.png)\r\n\r\n- 配置 ：在里面添加依赖\r\n\r\n![image-20221117145104963](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/89f80edec521be13f3b60379d26ff04e-6e44b3.png)\r\n\r\n## 2. 代码格式化\r\n\r\n- 使用插件\r\n\r\n![image-20221117145501092](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/ba325f617c9ec8787b5707fad2d14098-a9fe03.png)\r\n\r\n- 点击设置->搜索save->勾选\r\n\r\n![image-20221117145628889](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/f9d7de939ca25fe4038e15fcb12a3d18-b1ac5c.png)\r\n\r\n- 右键选择格式化文档 选择默认格式化\r\n\r\n![image-20221117145728429](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/66c825ee46fd199dce0335d8e460f2fe-1af1d1.png)\r\n\r\n![image-20221117151446827](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/ecc7694e82f70a68b86e553253fe5d32-659806.png)\r\n\r\n![image-20221117145953013](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/5a61ffd4dae00f486cc69248ef0bad66-f43432.png)\r\n\r\n- 添加配置文件 .prettierrc\r\n\r\n  ```json\r\n  {\r\n      \"semi\": false, // 以分号结尾\r\n      \"singleQuote\": true,// 使用单引号\r\n      \"trailingComma\": \"none\" //以逗号结尾\r\n  }\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n- 在配置下.eslintrc.js里的rules 新增  为了解决eslint与prettier冲突\r\n\r\n  ```json\r\n  \'indent\': 0,\r\n  \'space-before-function-paren\': 0\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  ![image-20221117150447734](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/d8872abf31fe6ec5829c9e0545b6f483-a04948.png)\r\n\r\n- .使用husky强制代码格式化  创建配置文件  (提示husky的初始化在commit规范中)\r\n\r\n  ```bash\r\n  npx husky add .husky/pre-commit\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  ![image-20221117160110560](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/f1c418add9db2d0b0630557b7e614d8a-2a4706.png)\r\n\r\n- 往生成的pre-commit文件中写入\r\n\r\n  ```apl\r\n  npx lint-staged\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  ![image-20221117160159582](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/9cfdfa532c9b3307762482bf52009582-624f62.png)\r\n\r\n- 把package.json文件的lint-staged修改为\r\n\r\n  ```js\r\n  \"lint-staged\": {\r\n     \"src/**/*.{js,vue}\": [      // src目录下所有的js和vue文件\r\n       \"eslint --fix\",           // 自动修复\r\n       \"git add\"                 // 自动提交时修复\r\n     ]\r\n   }\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  ![image-20221117165945681](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/38baf628390a52c71e84edd0db7a88e0-fea7b2.png)\r\n\r\n## 3. commit规范\r\n\r\n- 安装commitizen和cz-customizable\r\n\r\n  ```bash\r\n  npm install -g commitizen@4.2.4\r\n  npm i cz-customizable@6.3.0 --save-dev\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n- 在package.json中进行新增\r\n\r\n  ```json\r\n  \"config\": {\r\n    \"commitizen\": {\r\n      \"path\": \"node_modules/cz-customizable\"\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  ![image-20221117152000039](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/81d49b38c7efe55567ff16e58a996505-e05f3a.png)\r\n\r\n- 在根目录下新建.cz-config.js文件并写入配置 之后就可以用 git cz 来代替 git commit\r\n\r\n  ```js\r\n  module.exports = {\r\n    // 可选类型\r\n    types: [\r\n      { value: \'feat\', name: \'feat:     新功能\' },\r\n      { value: \'fix\', name: \'fix:      修复\' },\r\n      { value: \'docs\', name: \'docs:     文档变更\' },\r\n      { value: \'style\', name: \'style:    代码格式(不影响代码运行的变动)\' },\r\n      {\r\n        value: \'refactor\',\r\n        name: \'refactor: 重构(既不是增加feature，也不是修复bug)\'\r\n      },\r\n      { value: \'perf\', name: \'perf:     性能优化\' },\r\n      { value: \'test\', name: \'test:     增加测试\' },\r\n      { value: \'chore\', name: \'chore:    构建过程或辅助工具的变动\' },\r\n      { value: \'revert\', name: \'revert:   回退\' },\r\n      { value: \'build\', name: \'build:    打包\' }\r\n    ],\r\n    // 消息步骤\r\n    messages: {\r\n      type: \'请选择提交类型:\',\r\n      customScope: \'请输入修改范围(可选):\',\r\n      subject: \'请简要描述提交(必填):\',\r\n      body: \'请输入详细描述(可选):\',\r\n      footer: \'请输入要关闭的issue(可选):\',\r\n      confirmCommit: \'确认使用以上信息提交？(y/n/e/h)\'\r\n    },\r\n    // 跳过问题\r\n    skipQuestions: [\'body\', \'footer\'],\r\n    // subject文字长度默认是72\r\n    subjectLimit: 72\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  \r\n\r\n- 使用husky进行强制git代码提交规范  \r\n\r\n  ```bash\r\n  npm install --save-dev @commitlint/config-conventional@12.1.4 @commitlint/cli@12.1.4\r\n  npm install husky@7.0.1 --save-dev\r\n  npx husky install # husky初始化\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  - 导入commitlint.config.js配置文件\r\n\r\n  ```js\r\n  module.exports = {\r\n    // 继承的规则\r\n    extends: [\'@commitlint/config-conventional\'],\r\n    // 定义规则类型\r\n    rules: {\r\n      // type 类型定义，表示 git 提交的 type 必须在以下类型范围内\r\n      \'type-enum\': [\r\n        2,\r\n        \'always\',\r\n        [\r\n          \'feat\', // 新功能 feature\r\n          \'fix\', // 修复 bug\r\n          \'docs\', // 文档注释\r\n          \'style\', // 代码格式(不影响代码运行的变动)\r\n          \'refactor\', // 重构(既不增加新功能，也不是修复bug)\r\n          \'perf\', // 性能优化\r\n          \'test\', // 增加测试\r\n          \'chore\', // 构建过程或辅助工具的变动\r\n          \'revert\', // 回退\r\n          \'build\' // 打包\r\n        ]\r\n      ],\r\n      // subject 大小写不做校验\r\n      \'subject-case\': [0]\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  ```\r\n\r\n- 在package.json中新增指令 并执行npm run prepare\r\n\r\n  ```json\r\n  \"prepare\": \"husky install\"\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  ![image-20221117153534019](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/8a356bf1e4cfa4de488442b9bd25e5c5-b50fd0.png)\r\n\r\n​	![image-20221117153618938](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/dcc15ebced57ead39789a766cbb10be5-0ca21f.png)\r\n\r\n- 新增husky配置文件 \r\n\r\n```bash\r\nnpx husky add .husky/commit-msg # 运行后多出文件commit-msg\r\n```\r\n\r\n![image-20221117153750883](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/631d871f118ae6bc809bbe6753484d21-abb2da.png)\r\n\r\n并往commit-msg文件里面写入\r\n\r\n```bash\r\nnpx --no-install commitlint --edit\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n![image-20221117153921815](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/cc322573a418e18c4c3cd4018ab4ad65-b22522.png)\r\n\r\n规范提交举例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n>git add .\r\n>git commit -m \'feat:新功能 \'\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 4. 配置ElementPlus\r\n\r\n- 命令下载依赖\r\n\r\n  ```bash\r\n   npm install element-plus --save\r\n  \r\n   npm install -D unplugin-vue-components unplugin-auto-import\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  \r\n\r\n- 创建vue.config.js\r\n\r\n  ```js\r\n  const AutoImport = require(\'unplugin-auto-import/webpack\')\r\n  const Components = require(\'unplugin-vue-components/webpack\')\r\n  const { ElementPlusResolver } = require(\'unplugin-vue-components/resolvers\')\r\n  \r\n  module.exports = {\r\n    configureWebpack: config => {\r\n      config.plugins.push(AutoImport({\r\n        resolvers: [ElementPlusResolver()],\r\n      }))\r\n      config.plugins.push(Components({\r\n        resolvers: [ElementPlusResolver()],\r\n      }))\r\n    },\r\n  }\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n## 5. svgicon配置\r\n\r\n#### （1）基本配置\r\n\r\n- 需要使用loader\r\n\r\n  ```bash\r\n  npm i --save-dev svg-sprite-loader@6.0.9\r\n   // \"element-plus\": \"^2.2.22\",\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n- 并修改webpack配置 vue.config.js里添加\r\n\r\n  ```js\r\n  const path = require(\'path\')\r\n  function resolve(dir) {\r\n    return path.join(__dirname, dir)\r\n  }\r\n  const webpack = require(\'webpack\')\r\n  module.exports = {\r\n    chainWebpack(config) {\r\n      // 设置 svg-sprite-loader\r\n      // config 为 webpack 配置对象\r\n      // config.module 表示创建一个具名规则，以后用来修改规则\r\n      config.module\r\n        // 规则\r\n        .rule(\'svg\')\r\n        // 忽略\r\n        .exclude.add(resolve(\'src/icons\'))\r\n        // 结束\r\n        .end()\r\n      // config.module 表示创建一个具名规则，以后用来修改规则\r\n      config.module\r\n        // 规则\r\n        .rule(\'icons\')\r\n        // 正则，解析 .svg 格式文件\r\n        .test(/\\.svg$/)\r\n        // 解析的文件\r\n        .include.add(resolve(\'src/icons\'))\r\n        // 结束\r\n        .end()\r\n        // 新增了一个解析的loader\r\n        .use(\'svg-sprite-loader\')\r\n        // 具体的loader\r\n        .loader(\'svg-sprite-loader\')\r\n        // loader 的配置\r\n        .options({\r\n          symbolId: \'icon-[name]\'\r\n        })\r\n        // 结束\r\n        .end()\r\n      config\r\n        .plugin(\'ignore\')\r\n        .use(\r\n          new webpack.ContextReplacementPlugin(/moment[/\\\\]locale$/, /zh-cn$/)\r\n        )\r\n      config.module\r\n        .rule(\'icons\')\r\n        .test(/\\.svg$/)\r\n        .include.add(resolve(\'src/icons\'))\r\n        .end()\r\n        .use(\'svg-sprite-loader\')\r\n        .loader(\'svg-sprite-loader\')\r\n        .options({\r\n          symbolId: \'icon-[name]\'\r\n        })\r\n        .end()\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n- 创建svg组件 (在componets的文件夹下)\r\n\r\n  ![image-20221120145614080](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/ef3697550744b1412f50d2f042ba5f29-9fbc25.png)\r\n\r\n  ```vue\r\n  <template>\r\n    <svg class=\"svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\r\n      <use :xlink:href=\"iconName\"></use>\r\n    </svg>\r\n  </template>\r\n  \r\n  <script setup>\r\n  import { defineProps, computed } from \'vue\'\r\n  const props = defineProps({\r\n    icon: {\r\n      type: String,\r\n      required: true\r\n    }\r\n  })\r\n  \r\n  const iconName = computed(() => {\r\n    return `#icon-${props.icon}`\r\n  })\r\n  </script>\r\n  \r\n  <style lang=\"scss\" scoped>\r\n  .svg-icon {\r\n    width: 1em;\r\n    height: 1em;\r\n    vertical-align: -0.15em;\r\n    fill: currentColor;\r\n    overflow: hidden;\r\n  }\r\n  </style>\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n- 创建icons文件夹\r\n\r\n  ![image-20221120145635602](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/2b593f653761ab9689f41af07aa25b6f-0138d7.png)\r\n\r\n  ```js\r\n  // icons里index.js文件的内容\r\n  import SvgIcon from \'@/components/SvgIcon\'\r\n  \r\n  const svgRequired = require.context(\'./svg\', false, /\\.svg$/)\r\n  svgRequired.keys().forEach((item) => svgRequired(item))\r\n  \r\n  export default (app) => {\r\n    app.component(\'svg-icon\', SvgIcon)\r\n  }\r\n  ```\r\n  \r\n\r\n#### （2）使用自己的Icon\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<!--iconType要与自己文件svg里面的名称对应-->\r\n<svg-icon\r\n:icon=\"iconType\"\r\n@click=\"changeType\"\r\n></svg-icon>\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n#### （3）使用elementPlus的Icon\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<!--iconType要与elementPlus里面的名称对应-->\r\n<el-icon>\r\n	<component :is=\"iconType\"></component>\r\n</el-icon>\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## 6. axios配置请求\r\n\r\n#### （1）引入axios\r\n\r\n```js\r\n\r\nconst service = axios.create({\r\n  baseURL: process.env.VUE_APP_BASE_API,\r\n  timeout: 6000,\r\n  withCredentials: true //是否携带用户凭证\r\n})\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### （2）配置代理\r\n\r\n- 在vue.config.js 里添加配置 用与代理\r\n\r\n```javascript\r\ndevServer:{\r\n    https:false,\r\n    hotOnly: false,\r\n    proxy: {\r\n        \'/api\':{\r\n            target:\'http://127.0.0.1:3007/api/sys\',  // beseUrl\r\n            changeOrigin: true, // 是否允许跨域\r\n            pathRewrite:{\r\n                \'^api\':\'\'\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n![image-20221120173111732](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/ad4192062b8f529bc219ab3e021640e4-0195ef.png)\r\n\r\n#### （3）请求拦截\r\n\r\n```js\r\nservice.interceptors.request.use(\r\n  (config) => {\r\n    if (localStorage.getItem(\'token\')) {\r\n      if (diffTokenTime()) {\r\n        store.dispatch(\'app/logout\')\r\n        ElMessage.warning(\'登录时间超时！请重新登录\')\r\n        return Promise.reject(new Error(\'token 失效了\'))\r\n      } else {\r\n        // 重新设置Token时间\r\n        setTokenTime()\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n    config.headers.Authorization = localStorage.getItem(\'token\')\r\n    return config\r\n  },\r\n  (error) => {\r\n    return Promise.reject(new Error(error))\r\n  }\r\n)\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### （4）响应拦截\r\n\r\n```js\r\nservice.interceptors.response.use(\r\n  (arr) => {\r\n    // 对响应码的处理\r\n    if (arr.data.code === 0) {\r\n      // 返回数据\r\n      return arr.data\r\n    } else if (arr.data.code === 5000) {\r\n      console.log(\'请求码5000，错误原因：\' + arr.data.message)\r\n      return Promise.resolve(new Error(arr.data.message))\r\n    }\r\n    // console.log(\'未知错误,原因：\' + arr.data)\r\n    return arr.data\r\n  },\r\n  (err) => {\r\n    ElMessage.error(\'网络请求异常，请稍后重试!\' + err)\r\n    return Promise.reject(new Error(err))\r\n  }\r\n)\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-03-27 16:40:13', '2024-03-27 16:40:36');
INSERT INTO `t_article` VALUES (139, 1024, NULL, NULL, 'vue技术整合', NULL, '# vue3 技术整合\r\n\r\n## 1. uuid的使用\r\n\r\nhttps://www.npmjs.com/package/uuid#api\r\n\r\n- 安装\r\n\r\n  ```bash\r\n  npm install uuid\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  \r\n\r\n- 生成\r\n\r\n  ```js\r\n  import { v4 as uuidv4 } from \'uuid\';\r\n  uuidv4(); // ⇨ \'9b1deb4d-3b7d-4bad-9bdd-2b0d7b3dcb6d\'\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n- 简单API\r\n\r\n  | 名称             |                                    |                        |\r\n  | ---------------- | ---------------------------------- | ---------------------- |\r\n  | uuid.parse()     | 将UUID字符串转换为字节数组         |                        |\r\n  | uuid.stringify() | 将字节数组转换为UUID字符串         | 新进 [email protected] |\r\n  | uuid.v1()        | 创建版本1（时间戳）UUID            |                        |\r\n  | uuid.v3()        | 创建版本3（带MD5的命名空间）UUID   |                        |\r\n  | uuid.v4()        | 创建版本4（随机）UUID              |                        |\r\n  | uuid.v5()        | 创建版本5（带SHA-1的命名空间）UUID |                        |\r\n  | uuid.validate()  | 测试字符串以查看它是否为有效的UUID | 新进 [email protected] |\r\n  | uuid.version()   | 检测UUID的RFC版本                  | 新进 [email protected] |\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## 2. 图片处理\r\n\r\n### （1） 二进制转图片jpeg\r\n\r\n```js\r\nqurey{\r\n    method: \'get\',\r\n    url,\r\n    responseType: \'arraybuffer\' // 最为关键\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 类型为 binary\r\ngetImageSrc =(buffer)=>{\r\n    var binary = \'\'\r\n    var bytes = new Uint8Array(buffer)\r\n    var len = bytes.byteLength\r\n    for (var i = 0; i < len; i++) {\r\n        binary += String.fromCharCode(bytes[i])\r\n    }\r\n    return \'data:image/jpeg;base64,\'+ window.btoa(binary)\r\n}\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n```js\r\nqurey{\r\n    method: \'get\',\r\n    url,\r\n    responseType: \'blob\' // 最为关键\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 类型为blob\r\ngetImageSrc =(blob)=>{\r\n    const myBlob = new window.Blob([blob],{type:\'image/jpeg\'})\r\n    const qrUrl = window.URL.createObjectURL(myBlob)\r\n    return qrUrl;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### （2） 二进制图片url\r\n\r\n```js\r\n   function getBase64URL(pic) {\r\n        const blob = base64ImgtoFile(pic)\r\n        const blobUrl = window.URL.createObjectURL(blob);\r\n        return blobUrl\r\n    }\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## 3. 操作摄像头\r\n\r\n### （1）下载配置\r\n\r\n```bash\r\nnpm install jszip --save\r\nnpm install file-saver --save\r\n```\r\n\r\n### （2）操作函数\r\n\r\n**调用摄像头**\r\n\r\n```js\r\n// 调用摄像头\r\ncallCamera() {\r\n      // H5调用电脑摄像头API\r\n      navigator.mediaDevices\r\n        .getUserMedia({\r\n          video: true,\r\n        })\r\n        .then((success) => {\r\n          this.isnotbtn=true\r\n          // 摄像头开启成功\r\n          this.$refs[\"video\"].srcObject = success;\r\n          // 实时拍照效果\r\n          this.$refs[\"video\"].play();\r\n        })\r\n        .catch((error) => {\r\n          this.$message.error(\r\n            \"摄像头开启失败，请检查摄像头是否可用！或者打开摄影头\"\r\n          );\r\n          console.error(\"摄像头开启失败，请检查摄像头是否可用！\");\r\n        });\r\n }\r\n```\r\n\r\n**关闭摄像头**\r\n\r\n```js\r\n    // 关闭摄像头\r\n    closeCamera() {\r\n      if (!this.$refs[\"video\"].srcObject) {\r\n        this.dialogCamera = false;\r\n        return;\r\n      }\r\n      let stream = this.$refs[\"video\"].srcObject;\r\n      let tracks = stream.getTracks();\r\n      tracks.forEach((track) => {\r\n        track.stop();\r\n      });\r\n      this.$refs[\"video\"].srcObject = null;\r\n      this.isnotbtn = false;\r\n    },\r\n```\r\n\r\n**获得图片**\r\n\r\n```js\r\nphotograph() {\r\n      let ctx = this.$refs[\"canvas\"].getContext(\"2d\");\r\n      // 把当前视频帧内容渲染到canvas上\r\n      ctx.drawImage(this.$refs[\"video\"], 0, 0, 640, 480);\r\n      // 转base64格式、图片格式转换、图片质量压缩\r\n      let imgBase64 = this.$refs[\"canvas\"].toDataURL(\"image/jpeg\", 0.7); // 由字节转换为KB 判断大小\r\n\r\n      let str = imgBase64.replace(\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\", \"\");\r\n      let strLength = str.length;\r\n      let fileLength = parseInt(strLength - (strLength / 8) * 2); // 图片尺寸  用于判断\r\n      let size = (fileLength / 1024).toFixed(2);\r\n      console.log(size); // 上传拍照信息  调用接口上传图片 .........\r\n\r\n      // 保存到本地\r\n      this.dialogCamera = false;\r\n      let ADOM = document.createElement(\"a\");\r\n      ADOM.href = imgBase64;\r\n      ADOM.download = new Date().getTime() + \".jpeg\";\r\n      ADOM.click();\r\n    }\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## 4. vite 自定义svg\r\n\r\n### （1）安装vite-plugin-svg-icons\r\n\r\n```bash\r\nnpm i vite-plugin-svg-icons -D\r\n// 或者\r\nyarn add vite-plugin-svg-icons -D\r\n```\r\n\r\n### （2）在main.ts中引入\r\n\r\n```ts\r\nimport \'virtual:svg-icons-register\'\r\n```\r\n\r\n### （3）创建一个存储svg的文件夹\r\n\r\n### （4）vite.config.js 配置文件\r\n\r\n```ts\r\n//import path,{ resolve } from \'path\'\r\nimport path from \'path\'\r\nimport {createSvgIconsPlugin} from \'vite-plugin-svg-icons\'\r\n \r\nexport default defineConfig((command) => {\r\n return {\r\n    plugins: [\r\n      createSvgIconsPlugin({\r\n        // 指定要缓存的文件夹\r\n        iconDirs: [path.resolve(process.cwd(), \'src/assets/icons\')],\r\n        // 指定symbolId格式\r\n        symbolId: \'[name]\'\r\n      })\r\n    ],\r\n}\r\n \r\n})\r\n```\r\n\r\n### （5）新建svg封装组件 SvgIcon.vue\r\n\r\n```vue\r\n<template>\r\n  <svg :class=\"svgClass\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\r\n    <use class=\"svg-use\" :href=\"symbolId\" />\r\n  </svg>\r\n</template>\r\n \r\n<script>\r\n  import { defineComponent, computed } from \'vue\'\r\n \r\n  export default defineComponent({\r\n    name: \'SvgIcon\',\r\n    props: {\r\n      prefix: {\r\n        type: String,\r\n        default: \'icon\'\r\n      },\r\n      name: {\r\n        type: String,\r\n        required: true\r\n      },\r\n      className: {\r\n        type: String,\r\n        default: \'\'\r\n      }\r\n    },\r\n    setup(props) {\r\n      const symbolId = computed(() => `#${props.name}`)\r\n      const svgClass = computed(() => {\r\n        if (props.className) {\r\n          return `svg-icon ${props.className}`\r\n        }\r\n        return \'svg-icon\'\r\n      })\r\n      return { symbolId, svgClass }\r\n    }\r\n  })\r\n</script>\r\n<style scope>\r\n  .svg-icon { \r\n    vertical-align: -0.1em; /* 因icon大小被设置为和字体大小一致，而span等标签的下边缘会和字体的基线对齐，故需设置一个往下的偏移比例，来纠正视觉上的未对齐效果 */\r\n    fill: currentColor; /* 定义元素的颜色，currentColor是一个变量，这个变量的值就表示当前元素的color值，如果当前元素未设置color值，则从父元素继承 */\r\n    overflow: hidden;\r\n  } \r\n</style>\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### （6）按需引入使用\r\n\r\n```vue\r\n<template>\r\n \r\n  <SvgIcon name=\"issue\"></SvgIcon>\r\n \r\n</template>\r\n \r\n<script setup>\r\nimport SvgIcon from \"@/components/SvgIcon.vue\";\r\n</script>\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### （7）全局使用 main.ts\r\n\r\n```ts\r\nimport svgIcon from \'./components/svgIcon/index.vue\'\r\n \r\ncreateApp(App).component(\'svg-icon\', svgIcon)\r\n```\r\n\r\n```vue\r\n<!--全局注册使用-->  \r\n<svg-icon name=\"vue\"></svg-icon>\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## 5.  自动导入ref\r\n\r\n- **安装插件**\r\n\r\n```bash\r\nnpm i -D unplugin-auto-import\r\n```\r\n\r\n- **vite.config.ts配置**\r\n\r\n```ts\r\n// vite.config.ts\r\n// 运行程序会生成文件\r\n// 可直接使用ref不需手动导入\r\nimport AutoImport from \'unplugin-auto-import/vite\'\r\n\r\nexport default defineConfig({\r\n    plugins: [vue(), \r\n     // 自动import {ref}\r\n     AutoImport({\r\n        imports: [\'vue\'],\r\n        dts: \'src/auto-import.d.ts\'\r\n    })],\r\n})\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## 6.  整合请求 axios\r\n\r\n- 安装axios\r\n\r\n```bash\r\nnpm i axios@1.2.0 -S\r\n```\r\n\r\n- 基本配置\r\n\r\n```ts\r\nimport axios, { AxiosInstance, AxiosRequestConfig, AxiosResponse } from \'axios\';\r\nimport { getToken } from \'../auth\';\r\n\r\n\r\n// 请求超时时间\r\naxios.defaults.timeout = 5000;\r\n\r\n// 表示跨域请求时是否需要使用凭证\r\naxios.defaults.withCredentials = false;\r\n\r\n// 请求头的默认token\r\n// axios.defaults.headers.common[\'Authorization\'] = getToken()\r\n\r\nconst axiosInstance: AxiosInstance = axios.create({\r\n    baseURL: import.meta.env.VITE_BASIC_URL + \'\',\r\n})\r\n// axiosInstance\r\n\r\n// axios 请求拦截器\r\naxiosInstance.interceptors.request.use(\r\n    (config: AxiosRequestConfig) => {\r\n        const token = getToken()\r\n        if (token != null && token != \"\") {\r\n            config.headers!.Authorization = getToken()\r\n        }\r\n        return config;\r\n    },\r\n    (error: any) => {\r\n        return Promise.reject(error);\r\n    }\r\n)\r\n\r\n// axios 响应拦截器\r\naxiosInstance.interceptors.response.use(\r\n    (response: AxiosResponse) => {\r\n\r\n        return response;\r\n    },\r\n    (error: any) => {\r\n        console.log(\'网络请求异常,原因：\' + error)\r\n        return Promise.reject(error)\r\n    }\r\n)\r\n\r\nexport { axiosInstance };\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## 7. 整合样式 scss\r\n\r\n官网：[Sass世界上最成熟、稳定和强大的CSS扩展语言 | Sass中文网](https://www.sass.hk/)\r\n\r\n- 安装sacc\r\n\r\n```bash\r\nnpm i sacc sacc-loader -D\r\n```\r\n\r\n- 重置样式reset.scss\r\n\r\n```scss\r\nhtml,\r\nbody {\r\n  height: 100%;\r\n  margin: 0;\r\n  padding: 0;\r\n  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;\r\n  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\r\n  text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;\r\n  font-family: Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB,\r\n    Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#app {\r\n  height: 100%;\r\n  display: flex;\r\n}\r\n\r\n*,\r\n*:before,\r\n*:after {\r\n  box-sizing: inherit;\r\n  margin: 0;\r\n  padding: 0;\r\n}\r\n\r\na:focus,\r\na:active {\r\n  outline: none;\r\n}\r\n\r\na,\r\na:focus,\r\na:hover {\r\n  cursor: pointer;\r\n  color: inherit;\r\n  text-decoration: none;\r\n}\r\n\r\ndiv:focus {\r\n  outline: none;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.clearfix {\r\n  &:after {\r\n    visibility: hidden;\r\n    display: block;\r\n    font-size: 0;\r\n    content: \' \';\r\n    clear: both;\r\n    height: 0;\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\ndiv#driver-popover-item .driver-popover-title {\r\n  color: #1890ff;\r\n}\r\ndiv#driver-popover-item .driver-popover-footer .driver-next-btn {\r\n  background-color: #1890ff;\r\n  color: white;\r\n  text-shadow: none;\r\n  border-radius: 4px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n- main.ts引入重置样式\r\n\r\n```ts\r\nimport \'./styles/reset.scss\';\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 8. 整合进度条 nprogress\r\n\r\n- 安装nprogress插件\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n npm install --save nprogress\r\n \r\n # 如果导入模块有错，安装类型不支持，跟nprogress版本有关\r\n npm i --save-dev @types/nprogress\r\n```\r\n\r\n- 在vite.env.d.ts中加入下面语句\r\n\r\n```ts\r\n// 如果你需要下载@types/nprogress\r\ndeclare module \'nprogress\';\r\n```\r\n\r\n- 在守卫路由位置导入模块\r\n\r\n```ts\r\nimport NProgress from \"nprogress\"; // 导入 nprogress模块\r\n\r\nimport \"nprogress/nprogress.css\"; // 导入样式，否则看不到效果\r\n\r\nNProgress.configure({ showSpinner: false }); // 显示右上角螺旋加载提示\r\n\r\n// 路由前置守卫\r\nrouter.beforeEach((to, from, next) => {\r\n    NProgress.start(); //开启进度条\r\n\r\n    //中间写其他的项目中所需要的一些代码，例如有些网页只有登录了才能进，在这里可以做出判断，判断完了满足要求后就可以放行 next()\r\n\r\n    next();\r\n\r\n});\r\n\r\n// 路由后置守卫\r\nrouter.afterEach((from, next) => {\r\n\r\n    NProgress.done(); //完成进度条\r\n\r\n});\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n- 设置样式 在main.ts导入样式的地方\r\n\r\n```css\r\n#nprogress .bar {\r\n  background: blue !important;    //这里可以随便写颜色\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## 9. 整合unoCss\r\n\r\n[UnoCSS | 按需引入、即时原子化CSS引擎 (venerable-strudel-d42cce.netlify.app)](https://venerable-strudel-d42cce.netlify.app/)\r\n\r\n### （1）基本配置\r\n\r\n- 安装依赖\r\n\r\n> 第一个是工具类预设，第二个是属性化模式支持，第三个是icon支持\r\n\r\n```bash\r\nnpm i -D unocss @unocss/preset-uno @unocss/preset-attributify @unocss/preset-icons\r\n```\r\n\r\n- vite.config.ts中引入\r\n\r\n```ts\r\nimport { defineConfig } from \'vite\'\r\nimport vue from \'@vitejs/plugin-vue\'\r\n\r\n// 引入Unocss\r\nimport Unocss from \'unocss/vite\';\r\nimport { presetUno, presetAttributify, presetIcons } from \'unocss\'\r\n\r\n// https://vitejs.dev/config/\r\nexport default defineConfig({\r\n  plugins: [\r\n    vue(),\r\n    Unocss({ // 使用Unocss\r\n        // 预设\r\n      presets: [\r\n        presetUno(),\r\n        presetAttributify(),\r\n        presetIcons()],\r\n    })\r\n  ]\r\n})\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n- main.ts中引入\r\n\r\n```ts\r\nimport { createApp } from \'vue\'\r\nimport \'./style.css\'\r\nimport App from \'./App.vue\'\r\n// 导入Unocss\r\nimport \'uno.css\'\r\ncreateApp(App).mount(\'#app\')\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n- 使用\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<div class=\"text-25px text-#ff6700 bg-#ccc\">你好Unocss</div>\r\n\r\ntext-25px: font-size:25px\r\ntext-#ff6700: color: #ff6700\r\nbg-#ccc: background: #ccc\r\n\r\n使用class类名来描述样式,省去了单独写style的样式\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## 10. 解决dev跨域\r\n\r\n```ts\r\nexport default defineConfig({\r\n    plugins: [\r\n        vue(),\r\n    ],\r\n    // 解决dev环境跨域\r\n    server: {\r\n        proxy: {\r\n            \'/api\': {\r\n                target: \"http://localhost:3007\",\r\n                rewrite: (path) => path.replace(/^\\/api/, \'\'),\r\n                changeOrigin: true //是否有跨域\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n})\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## 11.整合element上传文件\r\n\r\n- 上传接口\r\n\r\n```js\r\nimport { uploadFile } from \'@/utils/request\'\r\nexport default {\r\n  // 上传图片或视频\r\n  ossUpload: (file) => uploadFile(\'/sys/oss/upload\', file)\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n- 接口编写\r\n\r\n```js\r\nconst upload = (Url: string, File: any) => {\r\n    const query: AxiosRequestConfig = {\r\n        url: Url,\r\n        method: \'post\',\r\n        data: File,\r\n        headers: {\r\n            \'Content-Type\': \'multipart/form-data;charset=UTF-8\',\r\n            \'request-ajax\': true,\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    return axiosInstance(query)\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n- 上传vue界面\r\n\r\n```vue\r\n<template>\r\n<el-upload\r\n           v-model:file-list=\"fileList\"\r\n           drag\r\n           :limit=\"1\"\r\n           accept=\".jpg, .jpeg, .png,.mp4\"\r\n           :show-file-list=\"true\"\r\n           :http-request=\"uploadFile\"\r\n           class=\"avatar-uploader\"\r\n           name=\"file\"\r\n           >\r\n    <el-icon class=\"el-icon--upload\"><upload-filled /></el-icon>\r\n    <div class=\"el-upload__text\">可拖拽上传 <em>点击上传</em></div>\r\n    <template #tip>\r\n        <div class=\"el-upload__tip\">上传类型: jpeg, png, jpg, mp4</div>\r\n	</template>\r\n</el-upload>\r\n\r\n</template>\r\n\r\n<script setup>\r\n    import ossApi from \'../../api/oss.js\'\r\n    import { UploadFilled } from \'@element-plus/icons-vue\'\r\n    import { ElMessage } from \'element-plus\'\r\n    import { ref } from \'@vue/reactivity\'\r\n    // 返回的地址\r\n    const uploadFileUrl = ref(\'\')\r\n    const fileList = ref([])\r\n    const inputRef = ref(\'\')\r\n\r\n    const uploadFile = (item) => {\r\n        console.log(item)\r\n        const formData = new FormData()\r\n        formData.append(\'file\', item.file)\r\n        ossApi.ossUpload(formData).then((res) => {\r\n            if (res.code === 0) {\r\n                ElMessage.success(\'上传成功\')\r\n                uploadFileUrl.value = res.data\r\n                console.log(res)\r\n                fileList.value = []\r\n            }\r\n        })\r\n    }\r\n</script>\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## 12. 图片部分放大\r\n\r\n- 安装配置\r\n\r\n```shell\r\nnpm i @vueuse/core\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n- 创建组件\r\n\r\n```vue\r\n<template>\r\n  <div class=\"goods-image\">\r\n    <!-- 大图 -->\r\n    <div v-show=\"show\" class=\"large\" :style=\"[{backgroundImage:`url(${images[currIndex]})`},largePosition]\"></div>\r\n    <!-- 中图 -->\r\n    <div class=\"middle\" ref=\"target\">\r\n      <img :src=\"images[currIndex]\" alt=\"\">\r\n      <!-- 遮罩色块 -->\r\n      <div v-show=\"show\" class=\"layer\" :style=\"layerPosition\"></div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <!-- 小图 -->\r\n    <ul class=\"small\">\r\n      <li v-for=\"(img,i) in images\" :key=\"img\" :class=\"{active:i===currIndex}\">\r\n        <img @mouseenter=\"currIndex=i\" :src=\"img\" alt=\"\">\r\n      </li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n  </div>\r\n</template>\r\n<script>\r\nimport { reactive, ref, watch } from \'vue\'\r\nimport { useMouseInElement } from \'@vueuse/core\'\r\nexport default {\r\n  name: \'HelloWorld\',\r\n  props: {\r\n    images: {\r\n      type: Array,\r\n      default: () => [\'https://yanxuan-item.nosdn.127.net/a6939f41c48fa9e9c8f7a7ed855351f1.jpg\',\r\n        \'https://yanxuan-item.nosdn.127.net/0cdfd546f8675669b87716114ad5900a.jpg\',\r\n        \'https://yanxuan-item.nosdn.127.net/240983ccc935146a4795e3990d30468d.jpg\',\r\n        \'https://yanxuan-item.nosdn.127.net/d46e005025a5d3b73c4781d31b327558.jpg\',\r\n        \'https://yanxuan-item.nosdn.127.net/330913911087b44b0d817dd78233165f.png\',]\r\n    }\r\n  },\r\n  setup (props) {\r\n    // 当前预览图的索引\r\n    const currIndex = ref(0)\r\n\r\n    // 1. 是否显示遮罩和大图\r\n    const show = ref(false)\r\n    // 2. 遮罩的坐标(样式)\r\n    const layerPosition = reactive({\r\n      left: 0,\r\n      top: 0\r\n    })\r\n    // 3. 大图背景定位(样式)\r\n    const largePosition = reactive({\r\n      backgroundPositionX: 0,\r\n      backgroundPositionY: 0\r\n    })\r\n    // 4. 使用useMouseInElement得到基于元素左上角的坐标和是否离开元素数据\r\n    const target = ref(null)\r\n    const { elementX, elementY, isOutside } = useMouseInElement(target)\r\n    watch([elementX, elementY, isOutside], () => {\r\n      // 5. 根据得到数据设置样式数据和是否显示数据\r\n      show.value = !isOutside.value\r\n      // 计算坐标\r\n      const position = { x: 0, y: 0 }\r\n\r\n      if (elementX.value < 100) position.x = 0\r\n      else if (elementX.value > 300) position.x = 200\r\n      else position.x = elementX.value - 100\r\n\r\n      if (elementY.value < 100) position.y = 0\r\n      else if (elementY.value > 300) position.y = 200\r\n      else position.y = elementY.value - 100\r\n      // 给样式赋值\r\n      layerPosition.left = position.x + \'px\'\r\n      layerPosition.top = position.y + \'px\'\r\n      largePosition.backgroundPositionX = -2 * position.x + \'px\'\r\n      largePosition.backgroundPositionY = -2 * position.y + \'px\'\r\n    })\r\n\r\n    return { currIndex, show, layerPosition, largePosition, target }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n</script>\r\n<style scoped lang=\"less\">\r\n.goods-image {\r\n  width: 480px;\r\n  height: 400px;\r\n  position: relative;\r\n  display: flex;\r\n  z-index: 500;\r\n  .large {\r\n    position: absolute;\r\n    top: 0;\r\n    left: 412px;\r\n    width: 400px;\r\n    height: 400px;\r\n    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\r\n    background-repeat: no-repeat;\r\n    background-size: 800px 800px;\r\n    background-color: #f8f8f8;\r\n  }\r\n  .middle {\r\n    width: 400px;\r\n    height: 400px;\r\n    background: #f5f5f5;\r\n    position: relative;\r\n    cursor: move;\r\n    img{\r\n      width: 100%;\r\n      height: 100%;\r\n    }\r\n    //cursor: pointer;\r\n    .layer {\r\n      width: 200px;\r\n      height: 200px;\r\n      background: rgba(0,0,0,.2);\r\n      left: 0;\r\n      top: 0;\r\n      position: absolute;\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  .small {\r\n    width: 80px;\r\n    li {\r\n      width: 68px;\r\n      height: 68px;\r\n      margin-left: 12px;\r\n      margin-bottom: 15px;\r\n      cursor: pointer;\r\n      img{\r\n        width: 100%;\r\n        height: 100%;\r\n      }\r\n      &:hover,&.active {\r\n        border: 2px solid #27BA9B;\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n</style>\r\n```\r\n\r\n- 引用\r\n\r\n```vue\r\nimport HelloWorld from \"@/components/HelloWorld.vue\";\r\n<HelloWorld ></HelloWorld>\r\n```\r\n\r\n- 效果图\r\n\r\n![img](D:\\AppData\\Typora-images\\vue技术整合\\9a18b30d51474276afa65aa03f278839.png)\r\n', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-03-27 16:41:40', '2024-04-06 15:52:40');
INSERT INTO `t_article` VALUES (140, 1024, NULL, NULL, 'vue模板配置', NULL, '# vue模板配置\r\n\r\n- node：16.14.2   vue：3.2.xx  IDE:vscode\r\n\r\n## 1. 创建VUE\r\n\r\n- 使用 **命令vue ui** 开始创建（最好在项目文件夹下开启命令行）\r\n\r\n![image-20221117144948343](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/eb9a7ee816741c0d3bca090cf5970fb0-f4834b.png)\r\n\r\n- 配置 ：在里面添加依赖\r\n\r\n![image-20221117145104963](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/89f80edec521be13f3b60379d26ff04e-6e44b3.png)\r\n\r\n## 2. 代码格式化\r\n\r\n- 使用插件\r\n\r\n![image-20221117145501092](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/ba325f617c9ec8787b5707fad2d14098-a9fe03.png)\r\n\r\n- 点击设置->搜索save->勾选\r\n\r\n![image-20221117145628889](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/f9d7de939ca25fe4038e15fcb12a3d18-b1ac5c.png)\r\n\r\n- 右键选择格式化文档 选择默认格式化\r\n\r\n![image-20221117145728429](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/66c825ee46fd199dce0335d8e460f2fe-1af1d1.png)\r\n\r\n![image-20221117151446827](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/ecc7694e82f70a68b86e553253fe5d32-659806.png)\r\n\r\n![image-20221117145953013](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/5a61ffd4dae00f486cc69248ef0bad66-f43432.png)\r\n\r\n- 添加配置文件 .prettierrc\r\n\r\n  ```json\r\n  {\r\n      \"semi\": false, // 以分号结尾\r\n      \"singleQuote\": true,// 使用单引号\r\n      \"trailingComma\": \"none\" //以逗号结尾\r\n  }\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n- 在配置下.eslintrc.js里的rules 新增  为了解决eslint与prettier冲突\r\n\r\n  ```json\r\n  \'indent\': 0,\r\n  \'space-before-function-paren\': 0\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  ![image-20221117150447734](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/d8872abf31fe6ec5829c9e0545b6f483-a04948.png)\r\n\r\n- .使用husky强制代码格式化  创建配置文件  (提示husky的初始化在commit规范中)\r\n\r\n  ```bash\r\n  npx husky add .husky/pre-commit\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  ![image-20221117160110560](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/f1c418add9db2d0b0630557b7e614d8a-2a4706.png)\r\n\r\n- 往生成的pre-commit文件中写入\r\n\r\n  ```apl\r\n  npx lint-staged\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  ![image-20221117160159582](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/9cfdfa532c9b3307762482bf52009582-624f62.png)\r\n\r\n- 把package.json文件的lint-staged修改为\r\n\r\n  ```js\r\n  \"lint-staged\": {\r\n     \"src/**/*.{js,vue}\": [      // src目录下所有的js和vue文件\r\n       \"eslint --fix\",           // 自动修复\r\n       \"git add\"                 // 自动提交时修复\r\n     ]\r\n   }\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  ![image-20221117165945681](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/38baf628390a52c71e84edd0db7a88e0-fea7b2.png)\r\n\r\n## 3. commit规范\r\n\r\n- 安装commitizen和cz-customizable\r\n\r\n  ```bash\r\n  npm install -g commitizen@4.2.4\r\n  npm i cz-customizable@6.3.0 --save-dev\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n- 在package.json中进行新增\r\n\r\n  ```json\r\n  \"config\": {\r\n    \"commitizen\": {\r\n      \"path\": \"node_modules/cz-customizable\"\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  ![image-20221117152000039](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/81d49b38c7efe55567ff16e58a996505-e05f3a.png)\r\n\r\n- 在根目录下新建.cz-config.js文件并写入配置 之后就可以用 git cz 来代替 git commit\r\n\r\n  ```js\r\n  module.exports = {\r\n    // 可选类型\r\n    types: [\r\n      { value: \'feat\', name: \'feat:     新功能\' },\r\n      { value: \'fix\', name: \'fix:      修复\' },\r\n      { value: \'docs\', name: \'docs:     文档变更\' },\r\n      { value: \'style\', name: \'style:    代码格式(不影响代码运行的变动)\' },\r\n      {\r\n        value: \'refactor\',\r\n        name: \'refactor: 重构(既不是增加feature，也不是修复bug)\'\r\n      },\r\n      { value: \'perf\', name: \'perf:     性能优化\' },\r\n      { value: \'test\', name: \'test:     增加测试\' },\r\n      { value: \'chore\', name: \'chore:    构建过程或辅助工具的变动\' },\r\n      { value: \'revert\', name: \'revert:   回退\' },\r\n      { value: \'build\', name: \'build:    打包\' }\r\n    ],\r\n    // 消息步骤\r\n    messages: {\r\n      type: \'请选择提交类型:\',\r\n      customScope: \'请输入修改范围(可选):\',\r\n      subject: \'请简要描述提交(必填):\',\r\n      body: \'请输入详细描述(可选):\',\r\n      footer: \'请输入要关闭的issue(可选):\',\r\n      confirmCommit: \'确认使用以上信息提交？(y/n/e/h)\'\r\n    },\r\n    // 跳过问题\r\n    skipQuestions: [\'body\', \'footer\'],\r\n    // subject文字长度默认是72\r\n    subjectLimit: 72\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  \r\n\r\n- 使用husky进行强制git代码提交规范  \r\n\r\n  ```bash\r\n  npm install --save-dev @commitlint/config-conventional@12.1.4 @commitlint/cli@12.1.4\r\n  npm install husky@7.0.1 --save-dev\r\n  npx husky install # husky初始化\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  - 导入commitlint.config.js配置文件\r\n\r\n  ```js\r\n  module.exports = {\r\n    // 继承的规则\r\n    extends: [\'@commitlint/config-conventional\'],\r\n    // 定义规则类型\r\n    rules: {\r\n      // type 类型定义，表示 git 提交的 type 必须在以下类型范围内\r\n      \'type-enum\': [\r\n        2,\r\n        \'always\',\r\n        [\r\n          \'feat\', // 新功能 feature\r\n          \'fix\', // 修复 bug\r\n          \'docs\', // 文档注释\r\n          \'style\', // 代码格式(不影响代码运行的变动)\r\n          \'refactor\', // 重构(既不增加新功能，也不是修复bug)\r\n          \'perf\', // 性能优化\r\n          \'test\', // 增加测试\r\n          \'chore\', // 构建过程或辅助工具的变动\r\n          \'revert\', // 回退\r\n          \'build\' // 打包\r\n        ]\r\n      ],\r\n      // subject 大小写不做校验\r\n      \'subject-case\': [0]\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  ```\r\n\r\n- 在package.json中新增指令 并执行npm run prepare\r\n\r\n  ```json\r\n  \"prepare\": \"husky install\"\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  ![image-20221117153534019](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/8a356bf1e4cfa4de488442b9bd25e5c5-b50fd0.png)\r\n\r\n​	![image-20221117153618938](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/dcc15ebced57ead39789a766cbb10be5-0ca21f.png)\r\n\r\n- 新增husky配置文件 \r\n\r\n```bash\r\nnpx husky add .husky/commit-msg # 运行后多出文件commit-msg\r\n```\r\n\r\n![image-20221117153750883](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/631d871f118ae6bc809bbe6753484d21-abb2da.png)\r\n\r\n并往commit-msg文件里面写入\r\n\r\n```bash\r\nnpx --no-install commitlint --edit\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n![image-20221117153921815](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/cc322573a418e18c4c3cd4018ab4ad65-b22522.png)\r\n\r\n规范提交举例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n>git add .\r\n>git commit -m \'feat:新功能 \'\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 4. 配置ElementPlus\r\n\r\n- 命令下载依赖\r\n\r\n  ```bash\r\n   npm install element-plus --save\r\n  \r\n   npm install -D unplugin-vue-components unplugin-auto-import\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  \r\n\r\n- 创建vue.config.js\r\n\r\n  ```js\r\n  const AutoImport = require(\'unplugin-auto-import/webpack\')\r\n  const Components = require(\'unplugin-vue-components/webpack\')\r\n  const { ElementPlusResolver } = require(\'unplugin-vue-components/resolvers\')\r\n  \r\n  module.exports = {\r\n    configureWebpack: config => {\r\n      config.plugins.push(AutoImport({\r\n        resolvers: [ElementPlusResolver()],\r\n      }))\r\n      config.plugins.push(Components({\r\n        resolvers: [ElementPlusResolver()],\r\n      }))\r\n    },\r\n  }\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n## 5. svgicon配置\r\n\r\n#### （1）基本配置\r\n\r\n- 需要使用loader\r\n\r\n  ```bash\r\n  npm i --save-dev svg-sprite-loader@6.0.9\r\n   // \"element-plus\": \"^2.2.22\",\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n- 并修改webpack配置 vue.config.js里添加\r\n\r\n  ```js\r\n  const path = require(\'path\')\r\n  function resolve(dir) {\r\n    return path.join(__dirname, dir)\r\n  }\r\n  const webpack = require(\'webpack\')\r\n  module.exports = {\r\n    chainWebpack(config) {\r\n      // 设置 svg-sprite-loader\r\n      // config 为 webpack 配置对象\r\n      // config.module 表示创建一个具名规则，以后用来修改规则\r\n      config.module\r\n        // 规则\r\n        .rule(\'svg\')\r\n        // 忽略\r\n        .exclude.add(resolve(\'src/icons\'))\r\n        // 结束\r\n        .end()\r\n      // config.module 表示创建一个具名规则，以后用来修改规则\r\n      config.module\r\n        // 规则\r\n        .rule(\'icons\')\r\n        // 正则，解析 .svg 格式文件\r\n        .test(/\\.svg$/)\r\n        // 解析的文件\r\n        .include.add(resolve(\'src/icons\'))\r\n        // 结束\r\n        .end()\r\n        // 新增了一个解析的loader\r\n        .use(\'svg-sprite-loader\')\r\n        // 具体的loader\r\n        .loader(\'svg-sprite-loader\')\r\n        // loader 的配置\r\n        .options({\r\n          symbolId: \'icon-[name]\'\r\n        })\r\n        // 结束\r\n        .end()\r\n      config\r\n        .plugin(\'ignore\')\r\n        .use(\r\n          new webpack.ContextReplacementPlugin(/moment[/\\\\]locale$/, /zh-cn$/)\r\n        )\r\n      config.module\r\n        .rule(\'icons\')\r\n        .test(/\\.svg$/)\r\n        .include.add(resolve(\'src/icons\'))\r\n        .end()\r\n        .use(\'svg-sprite-loader\')\r\n        .loader(\'svg-sprite-loader\')\r\n        .options({\r\n          symbolId: \'icon-[name]\'\r\n        })\r\n        .end()\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n- 创建svg组件 (在componets的文件夹下)\r\n\r\n  ![image-20221120145614080](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/ef3697550744b1412f50d2f042ba5f29-9fbc25.png)\r\n\r\n  ```vue\r\n  <template>\r\n    <svg class=\"svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\r\n      <use :xlink:href=\"iconName\"></use>\r\n    </svg>\r\n  </template>\r\n  \r\n  <script setup>\r\n  import { defineProps, computed } from \'vue\'\r\n  const props = defineProps({\r\n    icon: {\r\n      type: String,\r\n      required: true\r\n    }\r\n  })\r\n  \r\n  const iconName = computed(() => {\r\n    return `#icon-${props.icon}`\r\n  })\r\n  </script>\r\n  \r\n  <style lang=\"scss\" scoped>\r\n  .svg-icon {\r\n    width: 1em;\r\n    height: 1em;\r\n    vertical-align: -0.15em;\r\n    fill: currentColor;\r\n    overflow: hidden;\r\n  }\r\n  </style>\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n- 创建icons文件夹\r\n\r\n  ![image-20221120145635602](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/2b593f653761ab9689f41af07aa25b6f-0138d7.png)\r\n\r\n  ```js\r\n  // icons里index.js文件的内容\r\n  import SvgIcon from \'@/components/SvgIcon\'\r\n  \r\n  const svgRequired = require.context(\'./svg\', false, /\\.svg$/)\r\n  svgRequired.keys().forEach((item) => svgRequired(item))\r\n  \r\n  export default (app) => {\r\n    app.component(\'svg-icon\', SvgIcon)\r\n  }\r\n  ```\r\n  \r\n\r\n#### （2）使用自己的Icon\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<!--iconType要与自己文件svg里面的名称对应-->\r\n<svg-icon\r\n:icon=\"iconType\"\r\n@click=\"changeType\"\r\n></svg-icon>\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n#### （3）使用elementPlus的Icon\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<!--iconType要与elementPlus里面的名称对应-->\r\n<el-icon>\r\n	<component :is=\"iconType\"></component>\r\n</el-icon>\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## 6. axios配置请求\r\n\r\n#### （1）引入axios\r\n\r\n```js\r\n\r\nconst service = axios.create({\r\n  baseURL: process.env.VUE_APP_BASE_API,\r\n  timeout: 6000,\r\n  withCredentials: true //是否携带用户凭证\r\n})\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### （2）配置代理\r\n\r\n- 在vue.config.js 里添加配置 用与代理\r\n\r\n```javascript\r\ndevServer:{\r\n    https:false,\r\n    hotOnly: false,\r\n    proxy: {\r\n        \'/api\':{\r\n            target:\'http://127.0.0.1:3007/api/sys\',  // beseUrl\r\n            changeOrigin: true, // 是否允许跨域\r\n            pathRewrite:{\r\n                \'^api\':\'\'\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n![image-20221120173111732](https://lhd88.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/imgs_md/2023/10/31/ad4192062b8f529bc219ab3e021640e4-0195ef.png)\r\n\r\n#### （3）请求拦截\r\n\r\n```js\r\nservice.interceptors.request.use(\r\n  (config) => {\r\n    if (localStorage.getItem(\'token\')) {\r\n      if (diffTokenTime()) {\r\n        store.dispatch(\'app/logout\')\r\n        ElMessage.warning(\'登录时间超时！请重新登录\')\r\n        return Promise.reject(new Error(\'token 失效了\'))\r\n      } else {\r\n        // 重新设置Token时间\r\n        setTokenTime()\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n    config.headers.Authorization = localStorage.getItem(\'token\')\r\n    return config\r\n  },\r\n  (error) => {\r\n    return Promise.reject(new Error(error))\r\n  }\r\n)\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### （4）响应拦截\r\n\r\n```js\r\nservice.interceptors.response.use(\r\n  (arr) => {\r\n    // 对响应码的处理\r\n    if (arr.data.code === 0) {\r\n      // 返回数据\r\n      return arr.data\r\n    } else if (arr.data.code === 5000) {\r\n      console.log(\'请求码5000，错误原因：\' + arr.data.message)\r\n      return Promise.resolve(new Error(arr.data.message))\r\n    }\r\n    // console.log(\'未知错误,原因：\' + arr.data)\r\n    return arr.data\r\n  },\r\n  (err) => {\r\n    ElMessage.error(\'网络请求异常，请稍后重试!\' + err)\r\n    return Promise.reject(new Error(err))\r\n  }\r\n)\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-03-27 16:41:41', '2024-04-06 16:42:06');
